message.entry: The first input is invalid. If it is a cell array, a cell array of lidarScan objects is expected.
The second input is invalid. A cell array of finite [x y theta] vectors is expected.
If both scans and poses are provided as cell arrays, they are expected to have the same number of entries.
SLAM 맵 작성기가 제공된 입력값을 구문 분석할 수 없습니다. 입력 인수 없이 앱을 시작하십시오.
The specified rosbag, {0}, contains no scan topic of type sensor_msgs/LaserScan.
''slamMapBuilder''를 사용하여 rosbag을 가져오려면, ROS Toolbox 라이선스가 필요합니다.
